reviewText: Why is this unavailable?  The wrestling community has the video as a part of its folklore.  Every wresltler should watch this video
One of the best motivational videos out there for wrestlers. If it were available, I'd buy multiple copies. Needs to be released again!
Excellent video that shows the desire and will it takes to make a champion.  To accomplish what he did at the level that he did is truly amazing!!  I wish I could find this on DVD.
